rows.label: qev065308_MSG0001
rows.name:
These days, I spend my time helping out the other
Definians since they scattered.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065308_MSG0002
rows.name:
That said, troubles like Lyvia's here are outside my
area of expertise, so I'm relieved you showed up.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065308_MSG0003
rows.name: Can Definians feel romantic love as humans do?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: qev065308_MSG0004
rows.name:
Given practice, I think we could mimic it well enough,
but actually feeling it viscerally like you do?
I'm just not sure...[ST:wait ]
